%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20flag%20and%20stock%20market%20indicators%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6703e939a7031864927fd207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221060%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20stock%20rally%20could%20extend%20another%2015%25%20to%2020%25%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20country's%20equity%20indexes%20have%20jumped%20dramatically%20since%20Beijing%20announced%20major%20stimulus%20policies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20highlighted%20out%20still-low%20valuations%20and%20diminishing%20risk%20as%20tailwinds%20for%20a%20continued%20rally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blowout%20surge%20in%20China's%20stock%20market%20still%20has%20ways%20to%20go%2C%20with%20another%2015%25%20to%2020%25%20upside%20ahead%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20predicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20standout%20call%20for%20a%20market%20that%20has%20already%20impressed%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20Despite%20the%20short%20length%20of%20the%20Chinese%20rally%20to%20date%2C%20the%20MSCI%20China%20Index%20is%20now%20up%20more%20than%2034%25%20year-to-date%2C%20surpassing%20gains%20for%20the%20US%20benchmark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20significant%20gains%20in%20the%20equity%20market%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20two%20key%20factors%3A%20the%20catalyst%20of%20more%20substantial%20policy%20measures%20and%20the%20starting%20conditions%20of%20an%20oversold%20and%20under-positioned%20market%20backdrop%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20reference%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-aggressive-monetary-stimulus-interest-rate-rrr-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewide-sweeping%20set%20of%20policies%20Beijing%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduced%20in%20late%20September%2C%20signaling%20the%20government's%20seriousness%20about%20tackling%20China's%20lagging%20economy.%20Measures%20included%20liquidity%20boosts%2C%20interest-rate%20easing%2C%20and%20reserve-ratio-requirement%20cuts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mortgage-rate%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20forward%2C%20Goldman%20detailed%20four%20reasons%20to%20support%20its%2015%25-to-20%25%20upside%20forecast%20for%20Chinese%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Evaluations%20have%20room%20to%20expand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20if%20Beijing%20commits%20to%20its%20policy%20support.%20Even%20though%20they%20have%20recovered%20from%20a%20low%20of%208.4%20times%20forward%20earnings%2C%20valuations%20remain%20below%20a%20five-year%20mean%20of%2012.1%20times%2C%20Goldman%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20fiscal%20easing%20often%20corresponds%20with%20expanding%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EChina's%20recent%20policy%20announcements%20likely%20clamp%20down%20on%20investment%20risk.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20Beijing%20delivered%20its%20forceful%20stimulus%20blitz%2C%20the%20market's%20implied%20cost%20of%20equity%20stood%20at%20elevated%20levels%2C%20indicating%20lingering%20concern%20of%20downside%20risk.%20China's%20commitment%20to%20its%20new%20policies%20should%20ease%20this%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eearnings%20growth%20could%20pick%20up%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20the%20economy%20responds%20well%20to%20China's%20latest%20support%20measures.%20Goldman%20is%20optimistic%20in%20this%20outcome%2C%20estimating%20that%20the%20central%20bank's%20policy%20easing%20could%20uplift%20China's%20GDP%20by%2040%20basis%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20economists%20currently%20forecast%20GDP%20growth%20of%204.7%25%20and%204.3%25%20for%202024%20and%202025%20but%20note%20that%20the%20announced%20and%20indicated%20measures%20reduce%20downside%20growth%20risks%20inherent%20in%20recent%20monthly%20activity%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20equity%20%3Cstrong%3Epositioning%20is%20light%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20leaving%20room%20for%20more%20market%20entrants%20that%20could%20push%20stocks%20higher%2C%20Goldman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20risk%20appetite%20returning%20to%20onshore%20and%20foreign%20investors%2C%20market%20participation%20is%20rising%20from%20low%20levels.%20But%20even%20as%20traders%20snap%20up%20Chinese%20equities%2C%20their%20exposure%20still%20remains%20lax.%20For%20instance%2C%20mutual%20funds%20were%20310%20basis%20points%20underweight%20China%20at%20the%20end%20of%20August%2C%20Goldman%20said%3A%20the%20rally's%20jumpstart%20only%20deepens%20this%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20while%20Goldman%20said%20efforts%20so%20far%20have%20been%20very%20stocks-positive%2C%20it's%20not%20yet%20willing%20to%20declare%20that%20a%20structural%20bull%20market%20has%20begun.%20It%20cited%20that%20China%20continues%20to%20suffer%20major%20challenges%2C%20from%20low%20consumer%20spending%20to%20an%20indebted%20property%20market.%20Some%20analysts%20have%20cited%20that%20even%20more%20support%20is%20necessary%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-outlook-stimulus-fiscal-consumer-support-deflation-stephen-roach-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eespecially%20fiscal%20stimulus%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-stock-market-rally-outlook-bullish-drivers-stimulus-goldman-sachs-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728310580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6703e918198738e3a70ea3c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-stock-market-rally-outlook-bullish-drivers-stimulus-goldman-sachs-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20sto