alliance%20with%20the%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20to%20keep%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20out%20of%20power%20after%20the%202024%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20election%2C%20NC%20leader%20and%20ex%20Chief%20Minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20said%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20not...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20asked%20reporters%20when%20asked%20about%20an%20alliance%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20does%20it%20matter%3F%20If%20we%20all%20work%20for%20the%20same%20thing...%20for%20improvement%20in%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%20We%20can%20be%20rivals%20in%20elections%20but%20I%20have%20no%20objections.%20I%20am%20sure%20Congress%20will%20not%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%2C%2086%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20out%20any%20chance%20of%20staking%20claim%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20should%20his%20alliance%20win%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20be%20the%20Chief%20Minister...let%20this%20be%20clear.%20I%20have%20done%20my%20job.%20My%20problem%20will%20be%20-%20how%20can%20we%20make%20a%20strong%20government...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20had%20no%20problem%20approaching%20elected%20independent%20lawmakers%20for%20support%2C%20but%20warned%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20go%20beg%20before%20them.%20If%20they%20feel%20they%20can%20strengthen%20the%20state%2C%20then%20welcome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20allied%20under%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP%20was%20also%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20alliance%20but%20a%20seat-sharing%20deal%20could%20not%20be%20walked%20out%2C%20resulting%20in%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20party%20contesting%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20exit%20polls%20for%20tomorrow's%20counting%20of%20votes%20suggesting%20a%20hung%20Assembly%2C%20the%20PDP%20could%20end%20up%20playing%20'kingmaker'%20in%20J%26amp%3BK's%20first%20state%20election%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%20indicate%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%20will%20win%20the%20most%20seats%20but%20could%20fall%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2046%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20House.%20The%20PDP%2C%20which%20is%20projected%20to%20win%20between%20four%20and%2012%20seats%2C%20could%20hold%20the%20key%20-%20for%20either%20the%20NC-Congress%20or%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20NC-PDP%20tie-up%20was%20also%20mooted%20by%20Zuhaib%20Yusuf%20Mir%2C%20the%20latter's%20candidate%20for%20the%20Lal%20Chowk%20seat%20in%20Srinagar.%20Mr%20Mir%20said%20the%20PDP%20is%20open%20to%20joining%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20to%20ensure%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20grab%20power%20in%20the%20former%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPDP%20will%20have%20an%20important%20role%20in%20forming%20any%20secular%20government...%20we%20have%20said%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20any%20step%20to%20save%20the%20identity%20of%20Kashmir%20but%2C%20for%20this%2C%20it%20is%20important%20we%20form%20a%20government%20against%20BJP%20and%20not%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20the%20PDP%20and%20NC%20camps%20seems%20to%20share%20that%20view.%20PDP%20boss%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20daughter%2C%20Iltija%2C%20said%20any%20talk%20of%20an%20alliance%20before%20results%20are%20declared%20is%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%26quot%3B%20while%20Farooq%20Abdullah's%20son%20and%20senior%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20sought%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20a%20lid%20on%20all%20this%20premature%20speculation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20PDP%20leadership%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20extending%20support%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecular%20front%26quot%3B%20only%20once%20results%20are%20declared%2C%20Ms%20Mufti%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20official%20stand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20haven't%20extended%20support%2C%20