home-depot-12-foot-skeleton-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.homedepot.com%252Fp%252FHome-Accents-Holiday-12-ft-Giant-Sized-Animated-LED-Levitating-Reaper-24SV24287%252F328545039%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E12-foot%20Levitating%20Reaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFortunately%2C%20Skelly%20is%20sometimes%20available%20on%20The%20Home%20Depot's%20website%20and%20delivery%20is%20free.%20I%20relied%20on%20my%20PR%20contact%20at%20The%20Home%20Depot%20to%20get%20a%20review%20unit%20to%20test.%20(See%20our%20%26quot%3Balternatives%26quot%3B%20section%20below%20if%20you%20can't%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b0711a6-3591-4786-91da-a12e6b3e21f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESkelly%20arrived%20in%20a%20big%20truck%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%2012-foot%20skeleton%20is%20still%20in%20the%20box%20and%20on%20a%20pallet%20outside%20of%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004c9ca7031864927fa3c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20the%20delivery%20was%20pretty%20heavy-duty%20for%20box's%20relatively%20light%20weight%20(85%20pounds)%2C%20but%20my%20wife%20was%20happy%20for%20another%20pallet.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2012-foot%20skeleton%20didn't%20just%20arrive%20via%20the%20classic%20FedEx%20or%20UPS.%20Instead%2C%20a%20local%20delivery%20company%20called%20me%20the%20day%20before%20to%20make%20sure%20I'd%20be%20around%20during%20the%20delivery%20window.%20They%20told%20me%20they'd%20bring%20it%20between%209%20am%20and%201%20pm%2C%20though%20they%20were%20about%20half%20an%20hour%20late.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESkelly%20and%20his%20dog%20arrived%20in%20a%20large%20box%20truck%20and%20were%20wheeled%20to%20the%20base%20of%20my%20porch%20on%20a%20pallet%20jack.%20I%20had%20to%20sign%20several%20places%2C%20and%20the%20delivery%20folks%20took%20about%20a%20dozen%20photos%20before%20I%20was%20free%20to%20marvel%20at%20my%20new%20Halloween%20decorations.%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20heavy-duty%20delivery%20considering%20I%20get%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emattresses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20delivered%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20they're%20just%20tossed%20on%20my%20porch%20without%20even%20ringing%20the%20doorbell.%20The%20Skelly%20in%20the%20box%20weighs%20about%2085%20pounds.%20The%20pooch%20was%20under%2030.%20Since%20I%20live%20in%20a%20high-theft%20area%20and%20couldn't%20set%20them%20up%20right%20away%2C%20I%20dragged%20the%20bulky%20boxes%20inside.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6debb20-d6b1-46cd-ac59-7d18e3799b79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20setup%20took%20about%2045%20minutes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pieces%20of%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton%20are%20displayed%20on%20a%20lawn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004d173f2165d716dea0f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20step%20of%20the%20setup%20process%20was%20making%20sure%20I%20had%20all%20the%20pieces.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20the%20setup%20took%20a%20little%20over%2045%20minutes%2C%20and%20I%20did%20most%20of%20it%20on%20my%20own%2C%20though%20the%20instructions%20say%20to%20have%20two%20to%20three%20people.%20Before%20starting%20the%20assembly%2C%20I%20organized%20all%20the%20pieces%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20were%20all%20there.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20them%2C%20lettered%20A%20through%20V.%20Organizing%20them%20took%20me%20about%2010%20minutes.%20The%20instructions%20come%20in%20paper%20form%2C%20in%20an%20app%2C%20and%20printed%20on%20the%20box%20flaps.%20I%20chose%20to%20follow%20the%20box%20flap%20instructions%2C%20which%20were%20spot%20on.%20I%20tend%20to%20hit%20snags%20whenever%20I%20follow%20directions%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20assembling%20Skelly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20a%20skeleton%20shirt%20assembles%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004d603f2165d716dea160%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you're%20not%20wearing%20a%20skeleton%20shirt%20while%20assembling%20Skelly%2C%20what%20are%20you%20even%20doing%3F%20Note%3A%20If%20you%20look%20closely%20at%20its%20rear%20end%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20battery%20compartment.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20setup%20process%20was%20pretty%20simple.%20My%2010-year-old%20son%20helped%20me%20lift%20Skelly's%20upper%20body%20so%20I%20could%20attach%20the%20bracing%20cable%20and%20put%20it%20upright%20when%20I%20was%20done.%20My%20wife%20helped%20me%20position%20the%20upright%20skeleton%20perfectly.%20I%20liked%20that%20I%20could%20put%20the%20arms%20in%20various%20positions.%20I%20decided%20on%20a%20menacing%20wave%20with%20one%20arm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20tool%20I%20needed%20to%20set%20up%20Skelly%20was%20a%20screwdriver%20to%20remove%20the%20battery%20cover.%20It%20doesn't%20come%20with%20batteries%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20buy%20four%20C%20batteries%20or%20plug%20in%20the%20AC%20adapter.%20I%20went%20the%20battery%20route%2C%20and%20they%20only%20lasted%2048%20hours%20before%20the%20eyes%20just%20started%20blinking%20to%20indicate%20low%20battery.%20The%20battery%20compartment%20is%20easily%20accessible%20under%20the%20pelvic%20bone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Attaching%20the%20feet%20and%20legs%20to%20the%20base%20of%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20BILT%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004ea7a7031864927fa505%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22807%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20the%20BILT%20app%2C%20you%20can%20follow%203D%20interactive%20instructions%20to%20assemble%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton.%3Cp%3EBILT%20app%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20love%20interactive%20instructions%2C%20download%20the%20BILT%20app%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fbilt%2Fid879452214%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EiOS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.bilt.mobile%26hl%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAndroid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20While%20I%20didn't%20use%20it%2C%20I%20did%20look%20at%20the%2012-food%20skeleton%20on%20there%2C%20and%20the%20directions%20seemed%20more%20useful%20since%20each%20step%20features%20a%203D%20illustration%20you%20can%20rotate%20and%20zoom%20in%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22463cfa34-ac8d-4fa9-afca-98c1eece0c43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESecure%20and%20name%20your%20Skelly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20mulch%20is%20shown%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004f0e198738e3a70e7745%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20wife%20used%20black%20mulch%20to%20obscure%20the%20somewhat%20unsightly%20base%20and%20to%20add%20more%20weight%20for%20stability.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20narrow%20object%20that%20goes%2012%20feet%20straight%20up%20into%20the%20air%20will%20want%20to%20fall%20over.%20This%20was%20especially%20true%20when%20I%20set%20it%20up%20on%20a%20windy%20day.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20four%20extension%20poles%20that%20attach%20to%20the%20base%20and%20four%20stakes%20that%20go%20about%206%20inches%20in%20the%20ground.%20These%20should%20keep%20it%20stable%20enough%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20add%20sandbags%20or%20weights%20to%20the%20base.%20My%20wife%20spread%20a%2040-pound%20bag%20of%20black%20mulch%20over%20the%20base%20which%20weighed%20it%20down%20and%20helped%20with%20the%20aesthetics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20securing%20the%20skeleton%20was%20hard%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20a%20name%20was%20harder.%20You%20gotta%20give%20your%20Skelly%20a%20cute%2C%20original%20name%2C%20preferably%20one%20with%20a%20relevant%20pun.%20I%20agonized%20over%20it%20for%20days%20with%20my%20editors%20and%20family.%20Skelly%20Ripa%20was%20floated.%20Skellonc%C3%A9%20was%20another%20good%20one.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20I%20had%20to%20go%20with%20MaSkully%20Skullkin.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20particular%20affinity%20for%20the%20Home%20Alone%20star.%20I%20just%20loved%20how%20over-the-top%20the%20name%20is%20and%20how%20it%20has%20the%20double%20pun.%20If%20you%20get%20stuck%2C%20AI%20has%20some%20helpful%20ideas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff57bcf1-2f79-4fff-8a5e-e6e60f062b09%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20payoff%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22963%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%2012-foot%20skeleton%20shown%20at%20night%20with%20its%20eyes%20lit%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67004faa198738e3a70e77de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassersby%20have%20stopped%20to%20take%20photos%20of%20Skelly%20at%20all%20times%20of%20the%20day%20and%20night.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20moment%20we%20had%20MaSkully%20upright%2C%20a%205-year-old%20walked%20by%20with%20his%20mother.%20The%20kid%20stopped%20and%20just%20stared%20at%20the%20skeleton%20in%20wonder.%20He%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20LCD%20eyes%20light%20up%20and%20seem%20to%20follow%20you%2C%20which%20is%20an%20impressive%20touch.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20photo%20of%20it%20at%20night%2C%20so%20once%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20I%20went%20out%20to%20my%20front%20yard.%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20someone%20out%20there%20already%20taking%20a%20photo.%20He%20didn't%20notice%20that%20I%20came%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20assumed%20I%20was%20another%20passerby.%20%26quot%3BYou%20had%20the%20same%20idea%20as%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20take%20a%20photo.%20I%20love%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20had%20MaSkully%20Skullkin%20up%20for%20a%20week%20now%2C%20and%20we%20continue%20to%20catch%20folks%20enjoying%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c21b132-ee0f-430d-b94b-e4ef3e7434a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20a%20skeleton%20shirt%20assembles%20the%2012-foot%20skeleton.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670050d8198738e3a70e78f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20might%20want%20to%20wear%20gloves%20while%20assembling%20Skelly%20because%20there%20are%20sharp%20pieces.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20might%20want%20to%20wear%20protective%20gloves%20while%20as