lective%201%2C000%20miles%20of%20border%20between%20Russia%20and%20Lithuania%2C%20Estonia%2C%20and%20Latvia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithuania-intercepted-russia-military-supplies-sent-to-ukraine-instead-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728306041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6703be523f2165d716dec79e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithuania-intercepted-russia-military-supplies-sent-to-ukraine-instead-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lithuanian%20customs%20intercepted%20military%20supplies%20leaving%20the%20Russian%20exclave%20of%20Kaliningrad%2C%20bound%20for%20Moscow.%20It%20said%20it%20handed%20them%20to%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mjankowicz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithuania-intercepted-russia-military-supplies-sent-to-ukraine-instead-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Implement%20NRC%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20Says%20Union%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20political%20heat%20rises%20in%20poll-bound%20Jharkhand%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20incharge%20for%20the%20state%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20will%20implement%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%20the%20state%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren-led%20state%20government%20is%20favouring%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI%20emphasized%20that%20they%20are%20determined%20to%20protect%20'Roti%2C%20Mati%20aur%20Beti.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20going%20to%20release%20its%20election%20manifesto.%20This%20election%20is%20not%20only%20about%20making%20someone%20a%20CM%20or%20of%20power%2C%20but%20it%20is%20about%20saving%20Jharkhand.%20We%20are%20determined%20to%20protect%20'Roti%2C%20Mati%20aur%20Beti'.%20Due%20to%20the%20infiltrators%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20demography%20of%20the%20region%20is%20changing%20rapidly.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20tribal%20population%20in%20the%20Santhal%20region%20was%20more%20than%2044%20per%20cent.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%2028%20per%20cent.%20The%20population%20is%20badly%20affected%20by%20these%20infiltrators%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20accused%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20of%20favouring%20the%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%20is%20favouring%20the%20infiltrators%20for%20vote%20bank%20politics.%20We%20will%20implement%20the%20NRC%20in%20Jharkhand%20in%20which%20local%20residents%20will%20be%20registered%20and%20the%20intruders%20will%20be%20selected%20and%20thrown%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%205%2C%20the%20BJP%20released%20'Paanch%20Prana'%20for%20youth%20and%20women%20of%20Jharkhand%20as%20part%20of%20their%20election%20manifesto%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20promises%20announced%20by%20party%20are%20Yuva%20Sathi%2C%20Gogo%20Didi%20Yojana%2C%20Ghar%20Saakar%2C%20Laxmi%20Johar%20and%20'Assured%20Employment'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Gogo%20Didi%20Yojana%2C%20women%20will%20be%20given%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%202%2C100%20every%20month.%20Under%20the%20guarantee%20of%20assured%20employment%2C%20a%20promise%20has%20been%20made%20to%20provide%205%20lakh%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20in%205%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20under%20Ghar%20Saakar%20promise%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20a%20house%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20youth%20for%20preparing%20for%20competitive%20exams%20under%20Yuva%20Sathi%20scheme.%20The%20graduate%20and%20post%20graduate%20students%20will%20be%20provided%20with%20Rs%202000%20financial%20assistance%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20competitive%20exams.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20vacant%20posts%20in%20the%20state%20will%20also%20be%20filled.%20The%20recruitment%20process%20will%20start%20in%20the%20first%20cabinet.%20By%202025%2C%20the%20process%20of%201%20lakh%20government%20recruitment%20will%20be%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Paanch%20Prana%2C%20under%20Laxmi%20Johar%2C%20all%20the%20families%20of%20the%20state%20will%20be%20given%20Rs%20500%20for%20gas%20cylinders%20and%20two%20gas%20cylinders%20will%20be%20given%20free%20in%20a%20year%2C%20particularly%20on%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20is%20expected%20to%20hold%20elections%20for%20its%2081-member%20legislative%20assembly%20by%20December%202024%2C%20as%20the%20current%20government's%20tenure%20is%20set%20to%20end%20in%20January%202025.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20the%20election%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202020%20assembly%20election%2C%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20won%2030%20seats%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%2025%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728305940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fqf3h56m8_shivraj-chouhan-shraddh-poster_625x300_12_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-implement-nrc-in-jharkhand-says-union-minister-shivraj-chouhan-6736682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20incharge%20for%20the%20state%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20will%20implement%20the%20National%20R