raint%20Is%20Not%20Even%20On%20The%20Table%20Anymore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjj2ncuf8_israel_625x300_07_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year's%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20unleashed%20carnage%20on%20ordinary%20civilians%2C%20the%20aftermath%20of%20which%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20Today%20marks%20one%20year%20since%20that%20fateful%20morning.%20Both%20the%20attack%20by%20a%20non-state%20actor%20and%20the%20state%20response%20to%20it%20were%20unprecedented%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20sheer%20scope%2C%20firepower%20and%20destruction.%20Gaza%20has%20been%20flattened%20out%2C%20with%20millions%20of%20people%20internally%20displaced%20within%20a%20narrow%20Gaza%20strip.%20Israel%2C%20too%2C%20has%20lost%20some%201%2C200%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%3B%20this%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20over%20250%20people%20who%20were%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20forget%20that%20the%20date%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20also%20marked%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War.%20The%20gravity%20of%20the%20day%20and%20the%20need%20to%20beef%20up%20security%20should%20not%20have%20been%20lost%20on%20Mossad%2C%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20and%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF).%20But%20perhaps%20Israel%20was%20overconfident.%20So%20when%20the%20agencies%20were%20caught%20unawares%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20heading%20Israel's%20ultra-right%20government%2C%20naturally%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20with%20only%20one%20goal%20in%20mind%3A%20reoccupation%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20World%20Has%20Failed%20To%20Understand%20The%20Conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20carpet%20bombing%20of%20Palestine%20and%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20number%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20and%20leaders%2C%20the%20group%20survives%20a%20year%20on.%20It%20continues%20to%20hold%20around%20100%20hostages%20captive%20even%20now%2C%20hoping%20to%20use%20them%20as%20leverage%20for%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%20and%20release%20of%20their%20prisoners%20from%20Israeli%20jails.%20But%20Netanyahu%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20for%20negotiation.%20Already%2C%20he%20has%20extended%20his%20tenure%20to%20escape%20legal%20action%2C%20in%20the%20process%20subjecting%20himself%20to%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20rulings%20and%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(warrants).%20Those%20things%20matter%20little%20to%20him%20though%20-%20if%20anything%2C%20Netanyahu%20seems%20to%20be%20wearing%20this%20international%20criticism%20as%20a%20medal%20of%20honour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20community's%20approach%20to%20resolving%20the%20conflict%20has%20been%20flawed%20since%20the%20very%20beginning.%20The%20focus%20has%20always%20been%20on%20avoiding%20the%20escalation%20and%20expansion%20of%20the%20war%20without%20showing%20much%20commitment%20towards%20addressing%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20tensions%2C%20including%20the%20Palestinian%20issue.%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20both%20suffer%20from%20the%20Mutual%20Assured%20Destruction%20(MAD)%20syndrome%2C%20that%20is%2C%20in%20case%20of%20conflict%2C%20they'd%20strive%20for%20each%20other's%20complete%20destruction.%20Iran's%20quest%20for%20nuclear%20parity%20with%20Israel%20and%20its%20asymmetrical%20advantage%20and%20influence%20exercised%20through%20its%20proxies%2C%20the%20three%20or%20four%20'H's%20-%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Palestine%2C%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%2C%20Houthis%20and%20Kataib%20Hezbollah%20in%20Iraq%20-%20have%20been%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20worry%20for%20the%20Jewish%20state%20as%20well%20as%20its%20benefactors%20in%20the%20West%2C%20especially%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Neutrality'%20Of%20Arab%20Countries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Arab%20countries%20in%20the%20region%20are%20wary%20of%20Iranian%20power%20pursuits%20and%20projections%20-%20which%20is%20why%2C%20even%20as%20many%20nations%20continue%20their%20rapprochement%20with%20Iran%2C%20the%20ongoing%20Israeli%20campaign%20against%20its%20proxies%20does%20not%20raise%20many%20eyebrows.%20This%20was%20evident%20during%20the%20recent%20Iran-Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%20meeting%20in%20Doha%2C%20where%20the%20new%20Iranian%20President%2C%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian%2C%20met%20the%20Qatari%20Emir%20and%20Foreign%20Ministers%20of%20GCC%20countries.%20The%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20forthrightly%20claimed%20that%20his%20country%20was%20committed%20to%20resolving%20all%20differences%20with%20Iran.%20%26quot%3BWe%20seek%20to%20close%20the%20page%20of%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20forever%20and%20work%20towards%20the%20resolution%20of%20our%20issues%20and%20expansion%20of%20our%20relations%20like%20two%20friendly%20and%20brotherly%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gulf%20countries%20also%20assured%20Iran%20of%20their%20neutrality%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war%20and%20stated%20that%20they%20would%20not%20allow%20US%20bases%20to%20operate%20against%20Iran.%20How%20that%20will%20play%20out%20is%20a%20million-dollar%20question%2C%20given%20how%20many%20of%20these%20countries%20recently%20closed%20their%20airspaces%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20missiles%20Iran%20fired%20at%20Israel%20recently%20were%20neutralised%20by%20the%20US%20airbase%20in%20Jordan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Iran%20Responded%20With%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20bombing%20of%20the%20Iranian%20mission%20in%20Damascus%20led%20to%20a%20calibrated%20exchange%20of%20missiles%20and%20attacks%20and%20counter-attacks.%20Post%20that%2C%20Tehran%20was%20persuaded%20not%20to%20retaliate%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20since%20a%20ceasefire%20deal%20had%20been%20in%20the%20offing.%20The%20new%2C%20somewhat%20moderate%2C%20President%20of%20Iran%2C%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20reopen%20channels%20of%20communication%20with%20the%20West%20and%20the%20US%2C%20including%20its%20nuclear%20files%2C%20which%20explains%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20restraint%20and%20patience%26quot%3B%20Iran%20showed%20initially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20shocking%20execution%20of%20the%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah's%20political%20and%20military%20leadership%2C%20including%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20was%20left%20with%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20respond%2C%20lest%20it%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20mere%20Paper%20Tiger%20by%20its%20people%20and%20proxies.%20Hence%2C%20on%20October%201%2C%20it%20fired%20some%20181%20missiles%2C%20most%20of%20which%20were%20intercepted%20by%20the%20US%20and%20others%2C%20though%20some%20did%20penetrate%20Israeli%20territory%2C%20hitting%20Mossad%20and%20military%20establishments.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20information%20of%20this%20operation%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20shared%20through%20common%20interlocutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Oil'%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20called%20this%20escalation%20a%20direct%20attack%20by%20Iran%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20respond%20and%20retaliate%20at%20a%20time%20and%20place%20of%20its%20choosing.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20wants%20to%20attack%20Iranian%20nuclear%20installations%20-%20it%20had%20done%20so%20earlier%20too%2C%20though%20clandestinely%20-%20but%20US%20President%20Biden%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20this.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20reportedly%20planning%20to%20target%20a%20few%20oil%20installations%20and%20refineries.%20Already%2C%20oil%20prices%20have%20shot%20up%20by%20over%20%248%20per%20barrel%20and%20may%20even%20breach%20the%20steady%20band%2C%20impacting%20several%20economies%2C%20including%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20Israel%20is%20engaged%20on%20several%20fronts%20simultaneously%2C%20including%20Gaza%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Iran.%20Iraqi%20militia%20groups%20have%20also%20used%20UAVs%20and%20missiles%20to%20attack%20Israeli%20positions%2C%20stating%20that%20any%20attacks%20on%20Iranian%20fields%20will%20deprive%20the%20world%20of%20oil%20supplies%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20IDF's%20main%20priority%20in%20Lebanon%20is%20the%20elimination%20of%20Hezbollah.%20Heavy%20clashes%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20forcing%20nearly%20a%20million%20Lebanese%20and%20Syrian%20refugees%20to%20flee%20for%20safety.%20Israel%20feels%20that%20the%20relentless%20attacks%20by%20Hezbollah%20across%20the%20border%20into%20Northern%20Isreal%20were%20putting%20its%20sovereignty%20at%20risk%2C%20with%20over%2070%2C000%20displaced%20Israelis%20unable%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes.%20But%20even%20in%20leaning%20towards%20this%20logic%2C%20it%20fails%20to%20realise%20the%20consequences%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza%20to%20a%2020%20times%20bigger%20Palestinian%20population%2C%20being%20flung%20around%20from%20place%20to%20place%20under%20inhumane%20conditions.%20The%20Lebanese%20army%20has%20also%20been%20dragged%20into%20the%20war%20and%20has%20responded%20to%20attacks%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20urge%20adherence%20to%20the%20UNSC%20Resolution%201701.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Watches%20With%20Bated%20Breath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20community%20has%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20at%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20in%20Lebanon%20as%20intense%20firing%20continues%20across%20the%20Blue%20Line%20and%20areas%20observed%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Interim%20Force%20in%20Lebanon%20(UNIFIL)%20are%20breached.%20Lebanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Najib%20Mikati%20also%20continues%20to%20urge%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%2021-day%20ceasefire%20proposed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20France%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20uninterrupted%20humanitarian%20and%20relief%20supplies%20as%20his%20country%20has%20been%20already%20reeling%20under%20deep%20political%20uncertainty%20and%20financial%20crunch.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Iranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20on%20his%20recent%20visits%20to%20Beirut%20and%20Damascus%20promised%20humanitarian%20support%20and%20assured%20the%20disjointed%20Hezbollah%20and%20Hamas%20of%20their%20full%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20G7%20leaders%20have%20condemned%20Iran's%20missile%20attacks%2C%20they%20have%20issued%20a%20statement%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20create%20space%20for%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20along%20the%20Blue%20Line.%20The%20Arab%20League%20also%20expressed%20its%20concern%20and%20full%20support%20for%20Lebanon.%20As%20for%20Iran%2C%20it%20now%20appears%20to%20have%20abdicated%20its%20strategic%20restraint%20and%20has%20maintained%20that%20though%20it%20did%20not%20want%20to%20escalate%20the%20war%2C%20an%20attack%20by%20Israel%20would%20force%20it%20to%20respond%20in%20an%20unconventional%20manner.%20A%20rare%20Friday%20sermon%20by%20Ayatollah%20Khamenei%20underlined%20that%20sentiment.%20Some%20even%20argue%20that%20with%20its%20nuclear%20enrichment%20at%20threshold%20levels%2C%20Iran%20is%20capable%20of%20building%20small%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20a%20much%20shorter%20duration.%20And%20if%20Israel%20chooses%20to%20target%20in%20its%20next%20strike%20Iranian%20missile%20storages%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20headquarters%2C%20air%20or%20sea%20bases%2C%20or%20nuclear%20or%20oil%20and%20gas%20facilities%2C%20then%20that%20could%20push%20Iran%20to%20even%20block%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20further%20choking%20maritime%20trade%20and%20hydrocarbons%20transit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThings%20May%20Turn%20Complicated%20For%20India%2C%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20urging%20restraint%20and%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20Three%20of%20its%20ships%20remain%20in%20Iranian%20ports%20for%20some%20exercises.%20Indian%20naval%20assets%20have%20also%20been%20guarding%20sea%20lanes%20and%20commercial%20shipping%20since%20the%20Houthis%20attacked%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%20New%20Delhi%20shares%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20both%20Iran%20and%20Israel.%20The%20region%20-%20India's%20extended%20neighbourhood%20-%20is%20critical%20as%20any%20instability%20and%20security%20deficit%20will%20mean%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20three%20'E's%20-%20economy%2C%20energy%20supplies%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20roughly%209%20million%20expats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20stand%2C%20unless%20sanity%20prevails%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20we%20are%20heading%20irreversibly%20into%20an%20abyss%20of%20disaster%20that's%20being%20facilitated%2C%20primarily%2C%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20effective%20multilateral%20deterrence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amb%20Anil%20Trigunayat%20is%20a%20Distinguished%20Fellow%20at%20Vivekananda%20International%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728302100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjhnn46lo_israel_625x300_07_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Firan-and-israel-are-pushing-the-world-into-a-deep-abyss-6735810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20things%20stand%2C%20unless%20sanity%20prevails%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20we%20are%20heading%20irreversibly%20into%20an%20abyss%20of%20disaster%20being%20facilitated%2C%20primarily%2C%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20effective%20multilateral%20deterrence