n%20Ocean%20Region%2C%20which%20includes%20Sri%20Lanka.%20India%20has%20also%20granted%20a%20US%24100%20million%20rollover%20of%20Treasury%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20thankful%20for%20India's%20decision%20to%20provide%20support%20-%20Rs%2030%20billion%20in%20addition%20to%20US%24%20400%20million%20bilateral%20currency%20swap%20-%20which%20will%20be%20instrumental%20in%20addressing%20forex%20issues%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20bilateral%20measures%20announced%20are%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20RuPay%20card%20issued%20by%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%2C%20a%20financial%20services%20firmed%20owned%20by%20a%20consortium%20of%20Indian%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20assisting%20the%20Maldives%20with%20an%20infrastructure%20project%20for%20the%20Greater%20Male%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20both%20sides%20seem%20satisfied%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20Mr%20Muizzu's%20first%20bilateral%20visit%20to%20this%20country%2C%20the%20agreements%20signed%20and%20comments%20made%20reflect%20the%20growing%20bonhomie%20after%20the%20diplomatic%20spats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728300660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fnmojh3so_maldives-mohamed-muizzu-pm-modi-joint-statement_625x300_07_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-always-been-first-responder-pm-modi-meets-maldives-president-muizzu-6734473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20underlined%