k%20in%20Test%20matches%20and%20may%20surprise%20the%20opposition%20for%20a%20game%20or%20two%20at%20best.%20While%20one%20paper%20called%20the%20Indian%20batting%20%E2%80%9CBossball%E2%80%9D%20because%20the%20captain%20or%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20team%2C%20Rohit%2C%20had%20shown%20the%20way%2C%20some%20from%20the%20old%20powers%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9CGamball%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20Indian%20coach%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20wrote%20in%20his%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-test-batting-bazball-ind-ban-rohit-sharma-approach-wtc-final-icc-cricket-column%2Farticle68727293.ece%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20England%20batting%20approach%20changed%20completely%20under%20the%20new%20regime%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20McCullum%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20that%20Rohit%20has%20been%20batting%20like%20this%20and%20encouraging%20his%20team%20to%20do%20so%20as%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGambhir%20has%20only%20been%20coaching%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20so%20attributing%20this%20approach%20to%20him%20is%20foot-licking%20of%20the%20highest%20quality.%20Gambhir%20himself%20hardly%20ever%20batted%20in%20this%20fashion%20like%20McCullum%20used%20to%20do.%20If%20any%20credit%20is%20due%2C%20it%20is%20solely%20to%20Rohit%20and%20nobody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20using%20the%20words%20this-ball%20or%20that-ball%2C%20I%20would%20suggest%20using%20the%20skipper's%20first%20name%2C%20Rohit%2C%20and%20term%20it%20the%20%E2%80%9CGohit%E2%80%9D%20approach.%20Hopefully%2C%20brainier%20people%20will%20come%20up%20with%20a%20trendier%20name%20for%20this%20rather%20than%20the%20lazy%20option%20of%20calling%20it%20after%20%E2%80%9CBazball%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20India%20skipper%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728297540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0je13lf8_gautam-gambhir-rohit-sharma-ind-vs-ban_625x300_01_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskars-foot-licking-bombshell-on-gautam-gambhir-backers-says-gamball-6735613%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20claimed%20that%20the%20credit%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20aggressive%20approach%20during%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20belonged%20completely%20to%20the%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskars-foot-licking-bombshell-on-gautam-gambhir-backers-says-gamball-6735613%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Submit%20Income%20Tax%20Audit%20Report%20Today%20To%20Avoid%20Penalties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-audit-filing-deadline-extended-taxpayers-get-extra-week-until-october-7-6683892%5C%22%3Eextended%20the%20deadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20file%20income%20tax%20audit%20reports%20for%20FY%202023-24.%20Originally%20set%20for%20September%2030%2C%20the%20new%20October%207%20deadline%20offers%20businesses%20and%20professionals%20a%20reprieve.%20Experts%20warn%20that%20further%20extensions%20are%20unlikely.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnUnion%20Minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20was%20grateful%20for%20the%20extension%20in%20response%20to%20a%20request%20made%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CAssociated%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industries%2C%20Udhampur%E2%80%9D.%20On%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20thanked%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20for%20granting%20the%20extension%20and%20%26quot%3Bconceding%20the%20request%20and%20issuing%20the%20orders%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAssessment%20Year%202024-25.%20Thank%20you%20Smt%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20ji%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnsitharaman%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40nsitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20conceding%20the%20request%20and%20issuing%20the%20orders%20accordingly.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2%2F2%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20(%40DrJitendraSingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrJitendraSingh%2Fstatus%2F1840607108804620374%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20was%20the%20deadline%20extended%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnGaurav%20Gupta%2C%20Managing%20Partner%20of%20S%20G%20Taxman%20Solutions%2C%20explained%20that%20this%20year's%20extension%20stemmed%20from%20technical%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20exemption%20from%20using%20Digital%20Signatures%20for%20small%20business%20owners%20and%20professionals%2C%20particularly%20proprietorship%20firms.%20%26quot%3BSystems%20and%20processes%20were%20facing%20technical%20glitches%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Economic%20Times.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20GST%20numbers%20tied%20to%20PAN%20data%2C%20the%20government%20anticipated%20a%20significant%20volume%20of%20tax%20audits%20and%20expected%20system%20overloads%20near%20the%20original%20deadline.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EConsequences%20of%20missing%20the%20October%207%20deadline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSR%20Patnaik%2C%20Partner%20(Head%20-%20Taxation)%20at%20Cyril%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%2C%20warned%20that%20failing%20to%20meet%20the%20extended%20deadline%20could%20result%20in%20penalties.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tax%20audit%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20by%20September%2030%2C%20and%20filing%20can%20be%20done%20by%20October%207.%20Missing%20this%20deadline%20can%20lead%20to%20penalties%20under%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Patnaik%20said%2C%20as%20per%C2%A0ET.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpecifically%2C%20non-compliance%20with%20Section%2044AB%20may%20incur%20a%20penalty%20of%200.5%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20sales%2C%20turnover%2C%20or%20gross%20receipts%2C%20or%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%2C%20whichever%20is%20lower.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20those%20required%20to%20undergo%20a%20tax%20audit%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20file%20the%20audit%20report%20before%20submitting%20their%20income%20tax%20return%20(ITR).%20If%20this%20isn't%20done%2C%20the%20ITR%20will%20be%20considered%20defective.%20The%20deadline%20for%20filing%20ITRs%2C%20if%20a%20tax%20audit%20is%20applicable%2C%20is%20October%2031%2C%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EConsequences%20of%20missing%20the%20ITR%20deadline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20Parveen%20Kumar%2C%20Partner%20at%20Dewan%20PN%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20Co%2C%20missing%20the%20ITR%20deadline%20will%20force%20taxpayers%20to%20file%20a%20belated%20return%2C%20which%20can%20only%20be%20submitted%20until%20December%2031%20of%20the%20relevant%20assessment%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiling%20a%20belated%20ITR%20comes%20with%20several%20consequences%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20late%20fee%20under%20Section%20234F%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20(or%20Rs%205%2C000%20if%20the%20declared%20income%20exceeds%20Rs%205%20lakh)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterest%20on%20outstanding%20taxes%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInability%20to%20carry%20forward%20losses%20to%20future%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20explained%20that%20not%20filing%20an%20ITR%2C%20even%20if%20a%20tax%20audit%20report%20has%20been%20submitted%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20repercussions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20penalty%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20by%20the%20assessing%20officer%20under%20Section%20271F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterest%20charges%20under%20Section%20234A%20for%20outstanding%20tax%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20notice%20for%20reassessment%20under%20Section%20148%20for%20detailed%20scrutiny%20of%20income%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELosses%2C%20such%20as%20business%20or%20capital%20losses%2C%20cannot%20be%20carried%20forward%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20severe%20cases%2C%20prosecution%20may%20be%20initiated%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20for%20significant%20tax%20liabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20the%20overall%20ITR%20deadline%20could%20be%20extended%20further%2C%20possibly%20to%20November%207%2C%202024%2C%20given%20the%20upcoming%20Diwali%20festivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728297360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fpmohpqgo_income-tax-refund_625x300_01_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsubmit-income-tax-audit-report-today-to-avoid-penalties-6735461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20extended%20the%20deadline%20to%20file%20income%20tax%20audit%20reports%20for%20FY%202023-24.%20Originally%20set%20for%20September%2030%2C%20the%20new%20October%207%20deadline%20offers%20businesses%20and%20professionals%20a%20reprieve.%20Experts%20warn%20that%20further%20extensions%20are%20unlikely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsubmit-income-tax-audit-report-today-to-avoid-penalties-6735461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JJ%20Watt%20hilarious%20response%20as%20TJ%20Watt%20secures%20place%20in%20NFL%E2%80%99s%20club%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pu