iv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fl826vd9g_abu-maamar-_625x300_07_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20all%20hope%20in%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abu%20Maamar%2C%20sitting%20amid%20rubble%20in%20the%20small%20graveyard%20by%20the%20family%20house.%20Beneath%20the%20debris%2C%20she%20said%2C%20lay%20Saly's%20grave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20grave%20was%20not%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas'%20attack%20on%20Oct.%207%20killed%20around%201%2C200%20people%20in%20Israel%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20about%20250%20people%20were%20taken%20hostage%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20the%20declared%20goal%20of%20wiping%20out%20Hamas%2C%20has%20since%20killed%20at%20least%2041%2C500%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20has%20said%20its%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20is%20necessary%20to%20crush%20Hamas%2C%20which%20it%20accuses%20of%20hiding%20among%20the%20general%20Palestinian%20population.%20Hamas%20denies%20this.%20Israel%20says%20it%20tries%20to%20reduce%20harm%20to%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIRSTRIKE%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Oct.%207%2C%20Gaza%20had%20faced%20an%20extensive%20Israeli%20blockade%20following%20Hamas'%20takeover%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20in%202007.%20There%20was%20little%20work%20and%20imports%20were%20severely%20restricted%20but%20her%20family%20was%20settled%2C%20Abu%20Maamar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbu%20Maamar%20lived%20with%20her%20husband%20near%20her%20brother%20Ramez'%20family%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20spend%20much%20of%20her%20time%20with%20her%20nieces%20Saly%20and%20Seba%20and%20her%20nephew%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20bombing%20intensified%20near%20the%20house%20after%20Oct.%207%2C%20Ramez%20sheltered%20with%20his%20family%20at%20his%20in-laws'%20about%201%20km%20(0.6%20miles)%20away.%20It%20was%20hit%20in%20an%20airstrike%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Abu%20Maamar%20heard%20she%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20Nasser%20hospital%20in%20Khan%20Younis.%20There%20she%20saw%20Ahmed%2C%20then%204%2C%20and%20grabbed%20him%20by%20the%20hand.%20She%20found%20Saly%2C%20dead%2C%20in%20the%20mortuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20wake%20her%20up.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20she%20was%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20there%20that%20Reuters%20photographer%20Mohammed%20Salem%20took%20the%20picture%20of%20Abu%20Maamar%20cradling%20her%20dead%20niece%2C%20her%20body%20wrapped%20in%20a%20white%20sheet.%20The%20image%20was%20named%20World%20Press%20Photo%20of%20the%20year%20and%20won%20a%20Pulitzer%20Prize%20along%20with%20other%20Reuters%20images%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20and%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDISPLACEMENT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20it%20had%20attacked%205%2C000%20Hamas%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20from%20Oct.%207%20until%20Oct.%2017%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20airstrike%20that%20killed%20Saly.%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities%20said%20about%203%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20by%20that%20point%2C%20including%20940%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20strike%20that%20killed%20Saly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20comment%20six%20days%20after%20her%20death%20about%20the%20killing%20of%20another%20family%20in%20a%20different%20airstrike%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Israel's%20military%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20entrenched%20itself%20among%20the%20civilian%20population%20throughout%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20So%20wherever%20a%20Hamas%20target%20arises%2C%20the%20I