lkar'%20every%20time%20he%20invokes%20the%20man's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20Gully%20Gully%3A%20Travels%20Around%20India%20During%20The%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20by%20Aditya%20Iyer%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20Gully%20Gully%3A%20Travels%20Around%20India%20During%20The%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20by%20Aditya%20Iyer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F09ijasv_gully-gully_625x300_07_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cover%20of%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Gully%20Gully%3A%20Travels%20Around%20India%20During%20The%202023%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20by%20Aditya%20Iyer%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3ECourtesy%3A%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Every%20Score%20Except%2058%20And%2075'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20shares%20invaluable%20nuggets%20such%20as%20(and%20this%20is%20a%20precise%20translation%20from%20Hindi)%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Shri%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20has%20hit%20a%20hundred%20centuries%2C%20but%20the%20most%20important%20statistic%20no%20one%20knows.%20I%20will%20tell%20you.%20Between%200%20and%20100%2C%20he%20has%20made%20every%20score%20except%2058%20and%2075.%26quot%3B%20And%2C%20this%20too%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20give%20you%20another%20data%3A%20There%20are%20365%20days%20in%20a%20year.%20Apart%20from%201%20May%2C%20he%20has%20batted%20on%20the%20remaining%20364%20days%20of%20the%20calendar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20finally%2C%20it's%20Tendulkar's%20turn.%20And%20he%20receives%20tremendous%20applause%20after%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNamashkar.%20Good%20evening.%26quot%3B%20He%20waits%20for%20the%20cheers%20to%20end%20and%20then%20begins%20again%2C%20first%20thanking%20all%20the%20dignitaries%20present%20on%20the%20stage.%20Then%20he%20gets%20into%20the%20thick%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20indeed%20a%20special%20moment%20for%20me.%20I%20remember%20when%20Mr%20%5BAshish%5D%20Shelar%20and%20Mr%20%5BAmol%5D%20Kale%20%5Btreasurer%20of%20BCCI%20and%20president%20of%20MCA%2C%20respectively%5D%20both%20called%20me%20on%20behalf%20of%20MCA.%20They%20said%20they%20have%20this%20thought%20of%20having%20your%20statue%20inside%20the%20stadium.%20I%20was%20extremely%20delighted%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20react.%20I%20am%20truly%20humbled%20when%20I%20stand%20here.%20I%20go%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20there%20are%20thousands%20of%20images%20which%20come%20to%20my%20head%3B%20too%20many%20incredible%20memories.%20It%20is%20truly%20God's%20gift%20to%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20turf%20which%20has%20given%20everything%20to%20me%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20Sat%20In%20The%20North%20Stand'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20to%20tell%20a%20couple%20of%20stories%20which%20nobody%20has%20possibly%20heard.%20There%20are%20a%20number%20of%20things%20I%20have%20spoken%20about%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20which%20you%20have%20already%20heard.%20But%20my%20first%20visit%20to%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20was%20way%20back%20in%201983.%20I%20was%20only%20ten%20years%20old.%20West%20Indies%20had%20come%20to%20India%2C%20and%20this%20was%20after%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20-%20that%20excitement%20was%20there%20when%20West%20Indies%20came%20here.%20All%20my%20colony%20friends%20in%20Bandra%20-%20not%20ten-year-olds%20but%20my%20brother's%20friends%2C%20possibly%20thirty-to-forty-year-olds%20-%20they%20all%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20this%20match.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20it%20happened%20but%20a%20ten-year-old%20called%20Sachin%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20accompany%20them.%20So%2C%20I%20went%20along%20with%20them%2C%20took%20a%20train%20from%20Bandra%20and%20got%20off%20at%20Churchgate%2C%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20whole%20game.%20By%20the%20way%2C%20I%20sat%20in%20the%20North%20Stand.%20We%20all%20know%2C%20cricketers%20know%2C%20what%20North%20Stand%20is%20capable%20of%3A%20when%20they%20get%20behind%20a%20team%2C%20no%20opposition%20can%20stop%20India%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20was%20part%20of%20that%20North%20Stand%20gang%20and%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20noise.%20While%20I%20was%20on%20my%20way%20back%20home%20to%20Bandra%2C%20somebody%20said%20on%20the%20train%2C%20and%20I%20overheard%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAchcha%20manage%20kiya%2C%20na%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BI%20managed%20well%2C%20didn't%20I%3F%5D%26quot%3B%20What%20is%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eachcha%20manage%20kiya%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%3F%20We%20were%20twenty-five%20of%20us%20and%20we%20had%20only%20twenty-four%20tickets%20for%20the%20match.%20Then%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAchcha%20manage%20kiya%20toh%20kya%20kiya%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20%5BWhat%20did%20you%20manage%20well%3F%5D%26quot%3B%20Woh%20bola%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESachin%20ko%20chhupa%20ke%20leke%20aana%20pada%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BHe%20said%20he%20had%20to%20hide%20Sachin%20and%20take%20him%20inside%5D.%26quot%3B'%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Wankhede%20Was%20Different%20From%20Shivaji%20Park%2C%20Cross%20Maidan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20the%20front%20section%20of%20the%20audience%2C%20mainly%20MCA%20administrators%20and%20the%20like%2C%20are%20beside%20themselves%20with%20joy.%20They%20rain%20laughter%20and%20heavy%20applause%20on%20Tendulkar%2C%20so%20he%20smiles%20and%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20he%20can%20be%20heard%20again.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20sometimes%2C%20being%20vertically%20challenged%20can%20also%20be%20an%20advantage.%20I%2C%20of%20course%2C%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20after%20that%2C%20but%20before%2C%20I%20played%20whatever%20cricket%20I%20had%20played%20till%20then%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%2C%20Cross%20Maidan%2C%20Azad%20Maidan%3B%20lot%20of%20noise%2C%20crowd%2C%20thousands%20of%20guys%20playing%20around%20us.%20Then%20we%20come%20to%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20and%20suddenly%20it's%20quiet%2C%20lush%20green%3B%20that's%20when%20I%20figured%20out%20%3Cem%3Eki%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20there%20are%20many%20more%20gaps%20visible%20when%20you%20are%20batting.%20And%20there%20are%20just%20nine%20fielders%20on%20the%20field.%20%3Cem%3EAzad%20Maidan%20pe%20pata%20nahi%20lagta%20hai%20ki%20fielder%20iss%20match%20ka%20hai%20ya%20uss%20match%20ka%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BAt%20Azad%20Maidan%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20the%20fielder%20belongs%20to%20this%20match%20or%20another%20match%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Gavaskar%20Invited%20Sachin%20In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETendulkar%20is%20easily%20the%20most%20gifted%20cricketer%20of%20all%20time.%20But%20those%20gifts%20don't%20necessarily%20spill%20over%20to%20the%20field%20of%20storytelling%2C%20what%20with%20him%20often%20landing%20the%20punchline%20long%20before%20he%20has%20constructed%20the%20narrative%20around%20it.%20But%20there%20are%20stand-up%20comics%20who%20would%20kill%20to%20have%20the%20response%20he's%20now%20being%20showered%20with%2C%20as%20men%20and%20women%20fall%20over%20themselves%20in%20laughter.%20He%20strides%20on%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESo%2C%20yahaan%20pe%20pehli%20baar%20waisa%20realize%20hua%20ki%20there%20are%20only%20nine%20fielders%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20gaps%20hai%2C%20maar%20sakte%20ho%20neeche%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BIt%20was%20only%20here%20that%20I%20realized%20that%20there%20are%20gaps%20in%20the%20field%20and%20I%20can%20find%20them%20along%20the%20ground%20too%5D%20.%20.%20.%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20be%20a%20ball-boy%20in%20the%201987%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20I%20was%20sitting%20right%20here%20in%20front%20of%20the%20dressing%20room%20when%20a%20gentleman%20called%20Mr%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20invited%20me%20inside%20the%20dressing%20room.%20I%20can%20never%20forget%20that.%20He%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20corner%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EYe%2C%20aat%20ye%2C%20tula%20dressing%20room%20daakhavto%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BYou%2C%20come%20here%2C%20I'll%20show%20you%20the%20dressing%20room%5D.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20met%20a%20few%20players.%20I%20was%20fourteen%20then%2C%20if%20I%20am%20not%20mistaken.%20For%20a%20fourteen-year-old%20to%20actually%20be%20invited%20by%20his%20hero%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20was%20a%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20the%20very%20next%20year%2C%20I%20played%20for%20Mumbai.%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20with%20Sunil%20Gavaskar.%20But%20I%20remember%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20seat%20available%20in%20that%20dressing%20room%20because%20that%20%5BMumbai%5D%20team%20was%20a%20mega%20team%2C%20all%20established%20players.%20I%20think%2C%20if%20I%20am%20not%20mistaken%2C%20there%20were%20seven%20or%20eight%20India%20players%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven.%20So%2C%20I%20walked%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20and%20I%20am%20looking%20for%20a%20spot%20to%20sit.%20The%20far%20left-hand%20seat%20was%20vacant%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20I%20go%20and%20place%20my%20kit%20bag.%20Then%20I%20realize%20that%20it%20was%20SMG's%20%5BSunil%20Manohar%20Gavaskar%5D%20seat%2C%20you%20know%20everyone%20said%20ki%20'%3Cem%3EArre%2C%20ithe%20Gavaskarchi%20seat%20aahe%2C%20ithey%20basaaycha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BThis%20is%20Gavaskar's%20seat%2C%20sit%20here%5D.'%20So%2C%20I%20was%20happy%2C%20thrilled%2C%20and%20I%20go%20out%20to%20bat%20in%20my%20debut%20match%2C%20and%20I%20score%20a%20hundred.%20Not%20surprising%20because%20the%20seat%20was%20not%20used%20to%20being%20occupied%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20%5Bwhenever%20Gavaskar%20was%20around%5D%3B%20the%20crease%20was%20used%20to%20being%20occupied%20so%20I%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20follow%20in%20my%20hero's%20footsteps.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resounding%20wave%20of%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(%3Cs