22-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20(Image%20courtesy%20yurakrasil%2Fshutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20get%20a%20requirement%20from%20a%20company%2C%20we%20give%20them%20matching%20job%20profiles%20within%2024%20hours.%20Following%20this%2C%20you%20have%20the%20standard%20hiring%20process%20by%20a%20company.%20Once%20the%20company%20completes%20their%20rounds%20of%20tests%20and%20interviews%2C%20the%20person%20who%20is%20selected%20joins%20the%20company%20within%20a%20day.%20We%20are%20focussed%20on%20delivering%20the%20right%20job%20(for%20the%20candidate)%2C%20and%20the%20right%20candidate%20(for%20the%20company)%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20job%20profiles%2C%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20project%20managers%2C%20designers%2C%20mobile-based%20application%20developers%2C%20web-based%20application%20developers%2C%20the%20front%20end%2C%20back%20end%2C%20full%20stack%20developers%2C%20testers%2C%20etc.%20We%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20state%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20that%20are%20hiring%20talent%20through%20the%20robust%20online%20community%20they%20have%20developed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%