o%20invest%20in%20such%20facilities%20and%20must%20progress%20with%20the%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SheWork.in%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fdiverse-office-portrait-talented-indian-girl-2078917600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728099000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D368833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pooja%20Bangad%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SheWork%2C%20overcame%20family%20expectations%20to%20change%20women%E2%80%99s%20roles%20in%20tech.%20SheWork%20helps%20women%20return%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%20after%20breaks%2C%20fights%20for%20equal%20opportunities%2C%20and%20challenges%20the%20gender%20bias%20that%20holds%20women%20back%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20grow%20and%20succeed%20in%20their%20careers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Speaking%20up%20After%2025%20Years%3A%20How%20Education%20Helped%20This%20Survivor%20Break%20the%20Cycle%20of%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20violence%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20five-year-old%20once%20visited%20a%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Didi%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(elder%20sister).%20The%20older%20woman%20called%20the%20young%20girl%20into%20a%20room%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20undress%2C%20and%20she%20complied.%20What%20happened%20next%20would%20give%20the%20young%20girl%20sleepless%20nights%20for%20many%20years%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20child%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Allahabad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20did%20not%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20good%20touch%20and%20bad%20touch.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20that%20what%20had%20happened%20was%20wrong%20and%20she%20should%20speak%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299069%2Fdr-mahalakshmi-yn-acid-attack-survivor-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esexually%20abused%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20she%20was%2015%20years%20old%2C%20in%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20houses%2C%20on%20trains%2C%20and%20more.%20When%20she%20was%2010%2C%20while%20travelling%20by%20train%2C%20a%20man%20older%20than%20her%20father%20asked%20her%20to%20share%20his%20berth%20since%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20confirmed%20berths.%20He%20proceeded%20to%20put%20his%20hands%20in%20her%20pants%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20a%20burning%20sensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20years%20later%2C%20Priyatama%20Sharma%20has%20decided%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20other%20girl%20or%20child%20has%20to%20endure%20the%20kind%20of%20abuse%20she%20experienced.%20Married%20at%2020%2C%20even%20before%20the%20results%20of%20her%20undergraduate%20programme%20were%20out%2C%20she%20endured%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%20abuse%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20her%20ex-husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-30-at-20.56.34-1728047013.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Priyatama%20as%20a%20young%20girl%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-30-at-20.56.34-1728047013.jpeg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-30-at-20.56.34-1728047013-169x300.jpeg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-30-at-20.56.34-1728047013-500x889.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-30-at-20.56.34-1728047013-150x267.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368743%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPriyatama%20as%20a%20young%20girl%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20living%20in%20a%20cage.%20He%20would%20get%20me%20whatever%20I%20wanted%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20me%20to%20go%20outside%20and%20meet%20others.%20He%20disliked%20me%20wearing%20jeans%20and%20hit%20me%20when%20I%20wore%20it%20once.%20He%20was%20also%20against%20me%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyatama%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20free%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20abuse%2C%20she%20fought%20her%20way%20out%20through%20education%2C%20believing%20that%20it%20was%20her%20path%20to%20success%20and%20freedom.%20While%20working%20part-time%20jobs%2C%20she%20studied%20and%20is%20now%20a%20librarian%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Bhopal.%20She%20is%20happily%20married%20and%20living%20her%20best%20life%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20where%20she%20says%20her%20worries%20are%20just%20like%20anyone%20else%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%94%20concerns%20about%20career%20growth%20and%20health%2C%20vastly%20different%20from%20her%20life%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20these%20small%20stressors%20are%20what%20life%20is%20all%20about%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%E2%80%9D%20Priyatama%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20sexually%20abused%2C%20but%20I%20kept%20mum%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20o